data.description: Huge price drop to $318,000 AND $5,000 in seller concessions to be applied to closing costs, interest rate buy down or to reduce the purchase price to $313,000. You choose what is best for you. Introducing your dream home! This charming 2,174 sqft oasis comes with a Fantastic Surprise, a sparkling salt water pool with a waterfall and more. The HVAC and roof were recently replaced, State of the art security system stays with the home and solar screens help reduce the electric bill. The massive Primary bedroom and walk in closet is truly an owner retreat. This home also offers a spacious living room and open kitchen layout that makes entertaining a breeze. It does not stop there,step outside into your private back yard where you can enjoy those lazy summer days by the pool. Carefree living at its finest! Plus many more benefits and features you have to see. Do not miss the opportunity to call this place your own. Contact us today to schedule a showing.
